title: RKL Secure Reasoning Brief Telemetry
subtitle: Phase 0+1+2 telemetry from 18-agent system (Nov 17-26, 2025)
description: Research-grade telemetry from the Resonant Knowledge Lab Secure Reasoning Brief system - an 18-agent multi-agent system demonstrating Type III Secure Reasoning (defined in included white paper). Includes 9 artifact types tracking agent behavior, decisions, and quality metrics. Features Phase 2 enhancements: artifact ID linking and step-level timing (Unix ms precision).
